many Westerners today practice Buddhist meditation

416
00:18:16,458 --> 00:18:18,708
while maintaining their original religious identity

417
00:18:18,916 --> 00:18:21,291
a pattern of adoption rather than conversion

418
00:18:21,291 --> 00:18:23,791
that mirrors Buddhism's historical spread in Asia

419
00:18:24,416 --> 00:18:27,625
this pattern of adaptation rather than confrontation

420
00:18:28,041 --> 00:18:29,791
characterized Buddhism spread

421
00:18:30,125 --> 00:18:32,208
it preferred dialogue over debate

422
00:18:32,583 --> 00:18:36,125
inclusion over exclusion and synthesis over conquest

