these violent voices do not represent all of Buddhism

435
00:19:07,750 --> 00:19:08,916
far from it

436
00:19:09,666 --> 00:19:12,041
across the world most Buddhist monks

437
00:19:12,041 --> 00:19:13,333
teachers and practitioners

