00:20:08,708 --> 00:20:11,500
they didn't follow the Buddha's path of non attachment

461
00:20:11,791 --> 00:20:14,000
they clung desperately to nationalism

462
00:20:14,250 --> 00:20:18,000
they didn't seek to end suffering they perpetuated it

463
00:20:19,250 --> 00:20:21,500
this isn't Buddhism as the Buddha taught it

464
00:20:21,500 --> 00:20:23,875
it's Buddhism hijacked by the very forces

465
00:20:23,875 --> 00:20:26,166
it was designed to overcome fear

466
00:20:26,500 --> 00:20:28,541
attachment and delusion

