00:20:56,166 --> 00:20:59,250
Myanmar and Sri Lanka experienced British colonization

479
00:20:59,250 --> 00:21:00,958
that privileged certain ethnic groups

480
00:21:00,958 --> 00:21:02,375
and religions over others

481
00:21:02,541 --> 00:21:04,666
creating lasting social divisions

