00:21:05,916 --> 00:21:09,333
Japanese militarism emerged as a response to western

483
00:21:09,333 --> 00:21:11,208
imperial dominance in Asia

484
00:21:11,708 --> 00:21:14,333
colonial powers often used religious differences

485
00:21:14,333 --> 00:21:17,250
to implement divide and rule strategies

486
00:21:17,541 --> 00:21:19,333
hardening boundaries between groups

487
00:21:19,333 --> 00:21:21,000
that had previously coexisted

