00:21:29,416 --> 00:21:31,166
against perceived foreign threats

492
00:21:31,708 --> 00:21:34,083
the exceptions we examined Myanmar

493
00:21:34,083 --> 00:21:36,125
Sri Lanka wartime Japan

494
00:21:36,333 --> 00:21:37,500
all involved Buddhism

495
00:21:37,500 --> 00:21:39,583
becoming entangled with nationalism

496
00:21:40,333 --> 00:21:42,833
this fusion of religious and national identity

497
00:21:42,833 --> 00:21:44,625
creates a dangerous dynamic

