00:23:38,083 --> 00:23:39,416
this simple practice

536
00:23:39,458 --> 00:23:41,583
scaled across millions of practitioners

537
00:23:41,875 --> 00:23:43,125
creates a fundamentally

538
00:23:43,125 --> 00:23:44,708
different relationship to conflict

539
00:23:44,708 --> 00:23:45,625
than faith's focus

540
00:23:45,625 --> 00:23:47,083
primarily on belief

541
00:23:47,791 --> 00:23:48,833
Buddhist meditation

